{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C3037 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3037 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"pos":[618,638],"content":"Compiler Error C3037","linkify":"Compiler Error C3037","nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C3037","pos":[0,20]}]},{"content":"'var' : variable in 'reduction' clause must be shared in enclosing context","pos":[639,713]},{"pos":[720,860],"content":"A variable specified in a <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>reduction<ept id=\"p1\">](../../parallel/openmp/reference/reduction.md)</ept> clause may not be private to each thread in the context.","source":"A variable specified in a [reduction](../../parallel/openmp/reference/reduction.md) clause may not be private to each thread in the context."},{"content":"The following sample generates C3037:","pos":[867,904]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C3037 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-csharp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"article\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C3037\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C3037\"\nms.assetid: 9ba8a890-d3c7-4cce-93c5-d358e2bfad28\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\ntranslation.priority.mt: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C3037\n'var' : variable in 'reduction' clause must be shared in enclosing context  \n  \n A variable specified in a [reduction](../../parallel/openmp/reference/reduction.md) clause may not be private to each thread in the context.  \n  \n The following sample generates C3037:  \n  \n```  \n// C3037.cpp  \n// compile with: /openmp /c  \nint g_i;  \n  \nint main() {  \n   int i;  \n  \n   #pragma omp parallel private(g_i)  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   // #pragma omp parallel   \n   {  \n      #pragma omp for reduction(+:g_i)   // C3037  \n      for (i = 0 ; i < 10 ; ++i) {  \n         g_i += i;  \n      }  \n   }  \n}  \n```"}